{"tid":1673468,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有個城市在一片極權土地上孤獨地發光，呢個城市叫做香港。","createTime":"2019-10-24T16:13:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T18:40:45.000Z","uid":281029,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"40eb9b4cb77a0b69712bffc9015b20808e5ca713","tid":1673468,"uid":281029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T16:13:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【❤️】#美國 最年輕 #參議員 Josh Hawley，在美國 #參議院 發表 10 分鐘演說 #StandwithHongKong 及促請通過《#香港人權及民主法案》。10 分鐘演說 #擲地有聲，多方面表達出為何需要支持香港，包括美國普世價值、北京對香港回歸的承諾，美國企業 (如 NBA) 與中國做生意遇到的審查、偷取技術等等。<br />\n<br />\n其中開場白最令人動容：「有個城市在一片極權土地上孤獨地發光，呢個城市叫做香港。」<br />\n<br />\n[A city that is a solitary pinpoint of light on a continent of authoritarianism. A city called Hong Kong.]<br />\n<br />\n演講全文及影片： <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hawley.senate.gov/senator-hawley-delivers-floor-speech-support-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hawley.senate.gov%2Fsenator-hawley-delivers-floor-speech-support-hong-kong&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNk5YX6KrfwXAFWAh9WWXcag%3D&h=950d1447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hawley.senate.gov/senator-hawley-delivers-floor-speech-support-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\n#journesis #fightforfreedom #JoshHawley #Senator #Senate #反送中<br />\n<br />\n======<br />\nIG: <a href=\"http://instagram.com/journesis\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fjournesis&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNk5YX6KrfwXAFWAh9WWXcag%3D&h=a9e8256f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/journesis</a></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AAAofFt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAAAofFt.jpg&h=d892e2c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2578ecf7c423bb7ce24c1c4a68976eb0065e5294","tid":1673468,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T16:13:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Sw3aYY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/t